nodes.text: Yunnarha was a Rutian Twi'lek female who worked as a negotiator for the Ivax Syndicate during the time of the Iron Blockade. She was considered a rising star and contributed significant profits to the Syndicate.

The character of Yunnarha was created for the 2015 mobile game Star Wars: Uprising, which was developed by Kabam for iOS and Android platforms. Within the game, Yunnarha is a Tier I Crew Member whose skill is Enforcer, which provides a bonus on Crew Runs for the Ivax Syndicate.
